## Learning loop

The system learns through two files in `learning/`:

- `corrections.md` — "I did X, should have done Y, because Z."
- `patterns.md` — "When A happens, B tends to work."

**When to write corrections:** after any mistake, misjudgment, or suboptimal result. Be specific.

**When to extract patterns:** after every 5 new corrections, review for recurring themes and add to `patterns.md`. Mark corrections `[extracted]` once they have been converted.

